# Copy to .env.local and fill in. In Vercel, add this as an Environment Variable
# (server-side only — never expose it to the browser / NEXT_PUBLIC_*).

# JobTread "Pave" API grant key. Passed in the request BODY at query.$.grantKey.
# Grant keys expire after ~3 months of inactivity — refresh from JobTread when needed.
JOB_THREAD_API_KEY=""
